### Aegis crew API
### Crew = travelling production: tour managers, photographers,
### videographers, social media, FOH engineers. Not stage hands or volunteers.
### Run with REST Client extension. Replace cookie after sign-in.

@host = http://localhost:3000
@cookie = better-auth.session_token=...replace_after_signin...

### List — success
GET {{host}}/api/crew
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### List with filters — success
GET {{host}}/api/crew?search=mira&role=Tour%20manager&archived=archived
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### List — failure: unauthenticated
GET {{host}}/api/crew

### Create — success
# @name createCrew
POST {{host}}/api/crew
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{
  "name": "Mira",
  "role": "Tour manager",
  "email": "mira@example.com",
  "days": ["Friday", "Saturday", "Sunday"]
}

### Create — failure: validation (missing role)
POST {{host}}/api/crew
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{ "name": "No Role" }

### Create — failure: unauthenticated
POST {{host}}/api/crew
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Anon", "role": "ops" }

### Get one — success (replace ID with one from the list)
@crewId = REPLACE_WITH_ID
GET {{host}}/api/crew/{{crewId}}
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### Get one — failure: 404
GET {{host}}/api/crew/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### Update — partial: rename only
PATCH {{host}}/api/crew/{{crewId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{ "name": "Mira (renamed)" }

### Update — partial: clear phone with empty string
PATCH {{host}}/api/crew/{{crewId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{ "phone": "" }

### Update — partial: clear days with empty array
PATCH {{host}}/api/crew/{{crewId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{ "days": [] }

### Update — failure: empty body
PATCH {{host}}/api/crew/{{crewId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{}

### Archive — success (soft delete)
DELETE {{host}}/api/crew/{{crewId}}
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### Restore — success
DELETE {{host}}/api/crew/{{crewId}}?action=unarchive
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### Archive — failure: unauthenticated
DELETE {{host}}/api/crew/{{crewId}}
